[26/03/2018 12:44:29] <font color="#ffffff">(OLFATEAN)</font>
[26/03/2018 12:44:47] <font color="#ffff00">(R E)</font>
[26/03/2018 12:44:51] <font color="#ffff00">Oh...</font>
[26/03/2018 12:44:52] <font color="#ffff00">Hum...</font>
[26/03/2018 12:44:52] <font color="#ffffff">¿Qué ocurre?</font>
[26/03/2018 12:45:00] <font color="#ffff00">El cañón, defectuoso.</font>
